text: Bhai tu hai to harami bahut, tu aur kothari dono, Tu puch rha tha ki tere se kya dikkat hai, dikkat ye hai ki tu kothari harami ka dost hai. But I respect you for all the hard work you put in to maintain that CPI. Hopefully kabhi bahar milenge aur ek ache note se apni dosti shuru karenge. Cheers and goodluck aage ke lie. :D
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text: Bahut hi bhadwa hai tu saale, randi rona kar kar chaapna koi seekhe aapse. Baaki hopefully mumbai me milenge, aur raola ke flat me pade rahenge, apne speakers le aana, udhar hi laga lenge :p
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Loungaani bhaai, 
kya hi teddy bear aadmi ho bhaai tum, intern season me tumhara call sunkar jo kushi hui thi, aur first year me mast L20 me peeche baithkar bakchodi karne me maze aate the. It has been fun aur hopefully aage bhi milenge hi, lekin thank you for being a genuine friend, bhala ho prakhar ka jiski wjah se tumse mil paaya :p
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
aur madam, itna kya attitude hai ki tu ramola ko nai jaanti, ramola ko pura campus jaanta hai :p,
mujhe pata nai tha ki south delhi lite type ki ladki se aisi dosti ho jaegi, but sahi hai, maza aati hai tujhe chidhane me, bitching sessions me aur masala lene me GH ka :p
Mumbai me milte hain, phir continue karenge apna bitching session :p
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Gandhi dost,
Bhaai tere saath bahut maze aate hain, ab to iti puraani dosti hai ki BC yaad hi nai ki mile kaise the, but sir chaapu to aap hain hi, mujhe lagta tha ki dance kya chutiya cheez hia, lekin bhaai kya maza aata hai karne me, bhale hi bas 1 din sikhaya tune. Mumbai chal, udhar ramola ke flat ke hall ko dance room bana denge, gupta ke speakers laga ke reels banaenge dost. 
Baaki saale laundiya jaise gussa kyun ho jaata hai, bura laga koi cheez to bol na saamne se, randi saale. Love you <3
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Bhaai <3,
SAE se agar koi acha dost mujhe mila to wo tu hai, ek acha insaan. Mai zyada to nai likhunga but tu ek aisa banda hia jisse milkar hamesha chehre par khusi aa jaati hai, chahein jaisi bhi situation ho, tere pet ko uchalna miss karunga mai, patle mat hona dost.
aur kya ghatiya log lekar aaya hai tu har baar SAE me BC. Ek se ek tatti _/\_
love you, aur jai shree raam!
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text: Bhaai tumse theek se kabhi baat nai hui lekin hame ye pata tha ki ye banda ek leader hai, pata nai kyun kabhi theek se baat karne ki himmat nai juta pae ham, aakhri hi din baat hui tumse aur ye samajh aaya ki intellect level kitna high hai tumhara, itni baat nai hui lekin pir bhi tumhaara presence miss karenge. Shayad kabhi electon me tumhare lie vote dalne ka mauka mil jae, to hamara vote pakka smjhna dost <3
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Aur Alien Bhaai,
Apna to college se bhi ek saal purana rshta hai, hame aaj bhi yaad hai ki Advanced ke baad ghar aate hi tumko phoe karke apne number jode the, 200 ke upar dekh ke kya hi khushi hui thi bhaai <3.
Coaching ke doston me to ab tum hi bache ho. Apni utni baat to nai hoti ab but ye zarur pata hai ki zarurat ke samay hamesha ek dusre ke lie khade rahenge dono. Baaki gym jao thoda body shody banao aur ab jab bhi ghar aaenge to tumse milne zarur aaenge. :D
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Paateeeekkkkk,
Bhaai aise chup chaap reh ke chaapte rehna hamesha, also ye Parteekkkk wala naam hamne hi shuru kia tha :p
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
FIFA khelega ..?
bhaai jo maza tujhe harane me aata tha wo kahin aur nai aata tha :p
Mai to wait kar rha tha ki college khule aur fir tujhe FIFA me chodun, lekin saale taang de die tum to.
lekin bhaai thank you for being a genuine friend, milte hain college ke baad kabhi, FIFA khelenge
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Bhaai mai bowling nai karwaunga ab kabhi :'(
baaki bas ye malal hai ki tumse college khtm hote hote hi baatein ho pain, milte hain lucknow me, bakchodi karenge...
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text: Ramessss bhaaiiii, tum nai hote to shrey gaur mar chuka hota abhi tak mere haath se. Civil ke courses nikalwane ka bahut bahut shukriya. Bahut deserving aadmi ho bhaai tum, bahut kam hi log hain campus me jo fraud nai maarte, unmei se ek tum ho. Milte hain kabhi mumbai ya Banglore me. All the best bhaai.
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text: Bhaai jab bhi milo to hanste hue, aur shashwat bhaai bolne wale aur kaisi bhi situation me alag hi positivity dene wale bande ho yaar tum. aage bahut chaapoge tum dost life me. Best of luck dost.
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text: Mai to happy birthday hi nai bol paata, memoir likhna baut mushkil hai mere lie, but bas ye hai ki tu nai hota to shayad college itna acha nai hota. Kyunki itni harami dunia me ek bhola ramola ka hona bahut zaruri tha mere lie. But ab to bigaad hi dia hmne :p
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Aree Sirrrrrrrr, 
Kya boring FIFA khelta hai tu saale, na long shoot na bakchodwali tricks, bas kata kata ke gaand me ghus jao goal ki. Bhaai tere daaru bhand hone ke baad wala phase bhi dekha hai aur dinbhar mehnat karke ML ka code karne wala phase bhi, family trip par bhi chalenge ek baar. ML ki job lekar mumbai aa jaana jaldi se, udhar wapas FIFa khelenge <3
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text: Aadhe se zyada civil department ko sambhalne ka shukriya aapka. Tumhare taape hue assignment bahut yaad aaenge ðŸ˜›

text: bhaai tu hi tha jiske bharose TA me B lag gaya, warna to F tha mera, baaki team ke bharose rehta to lag gae hote mere, bahut kam log mile hain campus me jo fraud nai maarte, tu unmei se ek hai, aage ke lie best of luck :)
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Asati bhaiiii, 
MSE se civil wale 2 namoone the apan, maine to apni degree tere haathon me saunp di thi us din, jab tune bola the ki credits ho jaenge time se pure, us din ke baad kaise dosti badhti chali gai pata hi nai chala, aur naha lia kar saale, tere room ke andar ghusne ki himmat nai hoti thi. Ab IES nikal lo, phir to officer asati se milne aaenge.
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Areee bhaaiiiii, 
tu nai hota to mai to potata prince ka khoon hi kar deta 5th sem me, geoinfo ki lab tere aur ramesh patel ke bharose hi kaati hai maine puri...
Baaki IAS banoge jab tab milne aaenge!! bakchodi karenge
author: Shashwat  Shukla

text:
Aur Sir,
Maggu saale, itni BT di tune grades la lakar 3rd sem me ki mujhe branch hi change karni pad gai, lekin wahan bhi gupta bhadwa BT deta raha. Anyways, kaafi fun, GALAXY aur tu nai hota to pata hi nai chalta ki fimmaking jaisi cheezein bhi kar skte hain ham. Hopefully apna YT network hoga bahut bada usmei kuch kuch karenge. Mai tech head rahunga lekin :p
